1. Tell the user the purpose of the program and ask them for the name of the first item
2. Ask the user for the units of the first item
3. Ask the user for the cost of the item per unit
4. Calculate the cost of the item based on the unit
5. Ask the user for the name of the second item
6. Ask the user for the units of the second item
7. Ask the user for the cost of the  second item per unit
8. Calculate the cost of the item based on the unit
9. Output name of items, amount, price per unit and subtotal price for the first item
10. Repeat step 9 for second item
11. Output the total price
12. Thank the user for using the program